                  <p class="text-justify">You may contact us at any time and request: (i) that your information will be deleted (including to delete your account); (ii) to change any information we collected about you; (iii) to know what information we have collected about you; (iv) any other request or inquiry regarding your information, your privacy or your rights as you are entitled under applicable law from time to time; (v) express a concern you have about our use of your personal information; (vi) have us transmit any personal information directly to another organization, in certain circumstances; or (vii) lodge a complaint with a competent data protection authority.</p>
                  <p class="text-justify">Please direct all such inquiries to: <a href="mailto:dpo@breachreport.com">dpo@breachreport.com</a></p>
